更快乐 更健康 更成功

57
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:51,900
Why isn't everyone a benefit finder?
为什么不是人人都是积极者？

58
00:03:51,910 --> 00:03:53,530
Why aren't we all optimists?
为什么我们不都是乐观主义者？

59
00:03:54,010 --> 00:03:55,040
If it pays,
如果它是有回报的

60
00:03:55,340 --> 00:03:58,020
in both the ultimate currency- the currency of happiness
用终极货币形式 以幸福来回报

61
00:03:58,250 --> 00:04:02,760
as well as in hard currency- success currency?
也用硬货币来 以成功来回报？

62
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:06,570
Why are not more people benefit finders?
为什么没有更多的积极者？

63
00:04:06,790 --> 00:04:09,700
And the answer to that was,to great extent,
问题的答案 在很大程度上

64
00:04:09,880 --> 00:04:11,050
because of the media.
是因为媒体的原故

65
00:04:11,370 --> 00:04:14,840
What we have in the media is magnifying,zooming in,
媒体正在放大 聚焦

66
00:04:15,060 --> 00:04:20,140
magnifying the negative,maximizing it,
放大消极的东西 使其最大化

67
00:04:20,370 --> 00:04:22,710
having it take the entire screen,the entire page,
由它占据整个屏幕 整个版面

68
00:04:22,930 --> 00:04:25,510
while minimizing the positives.
同时最小化积极的东西

69
00:04:25,970 --> 00:04:31,100
And in many ways,the media makes fault finders out of us.
在很多方面 媒体把我们变成消极者

70
00:04:31,510 --> 00:04:33,790
And we need to counter that. How do we counter that?
而我们需要反击 如何反击？

71
00:04:33,980 --> 00:04:38,360
On the macro level,by having good news channels,for example.
宏观层面上可以收看好的新闻频道

72
00:04:38,770 --> 00:04:41,740
On the micro level,by having more inspiring art.
微观层面上可以培育富有启发性的艺术

73
00:04:42,070 --> 00:04:46,100
Art throughout history has changed the world-
艺术在历史进程中改变了世界

74
00:04:46,820 --> 00:04:48,350
whether it was during the dark ages,
不论是在黑暗年代

75
00:04:48,550 --> 00:04:50,160
at the transition to the Renaissance,
在向文艺复兴过度的时期

76
00:04:50,390 --> 00:04:55,220
whether it was during 18th and 19th century with Romantic artists
或者是在18和19世纪兴起的浪漫艺术家

77
00:04:56,810 --> 00:04:58,920
and paving the road to freedom,
致力铺设通向自由之路

78
00:04:59,180 --> 00:05:08,610
whether it was in mid 1930s and 40s with the Renaissance
亦或是上世纪三四十年代

79
00:05:08,810 --> 00:05:12,110
in many ways of Hollywood,bringing more hope to people.
好莱坞的复兴 带给人们更多希望

80
00:05:12,330 --> 00:05:14,280
So art plays a very important role,
艺术扮演着非常重要的角色

81
00:05:14,490 --> 00:05:16,510
and hopefully,will continue to do so.
希望能继续如此

82
00:05:16,770 --> 00:05:19,760
So then we talked about the global level,the macro level.
然后我们谈到大的层面 宏观层面

83
00:05:19,950 --> 00:05:21,120
On the micro level,
在微观层面上

84
00:05:21,330 --> 00:05:24,490
we talked about not waiting for bad things to happen,
我们谈到不要坐等坏事发生

85
00:05:24,680 --> 00:05:25,350
for tragedy,
不要等悲剧

86
00:05:25,510 --> 00:05:28,670
for something external to happen for us to be grateful.
或等外界有事发生 我们才知感激

87
00:05:28,890 --> 00:05:31,050
Because when we are grateful,by definition,
因为我们感激 就其定义而言

88
00:05:31,220 --> 00:05:33,710
we don't take something for granted.
就是不以某事为理所当然

89
00:05:34,190 --> 00:05:38,170
