141
00:08:19,020 --> 00:08:22,900
And it's only through that,that over time,over time,
只有这样 经过一段时间

142
00:08:23,160 --> 00:08:26,400
you'll begin to see more and more of the positive in the world
你才能开始越来越多地看到世界的积极方面

143
00:08:26,620 --> 00:08:28,690
and counter the current schema
才能反击当下禁锢着

144
00:08:28,910 --> 00:08:33,480
that most of us have literally been imprisoned by,
大多数人的思维方式

145
00:08:33,700 --> 00:08:35,280
the fault finder schema.
