但尝试一下 起码尝试21天或一个月

156
00:09:04,520 --> 00:09:07,400
Next week is going to be your task
这也是你们下周的任务

157
00:09:07,750 --> 00:09:11,690
as part of your weekly assignment.
作为每周任务的一部分

158
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:16,030
But start today. Don't wait. No other way to change. Because
从今天开始 不要等 实现改变没有他法

159
00:09:16,250 --> 00:09:21,970
what you are doing is gradually chipping away the excess stone.
因为你所做的是一点点凿掉多余的石头

160
00:09:22,230 --> 00:09:25,110
That excess stone,that limitation that has been put on us
那多余的石头 那些强加给我们的限制

161
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:28,390
by the schema all around us,
例如通过周围的观念

162
00:09:28,660 --> 00:09:33,630
by the news that you read this morning,by most conversations,
