Again,write it in a letter or by phone or in person.
写信 致电或面对面说都可以

289
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:18,870
One of the most effective interventions out there today
当今最有效的一种干预形式

290
00:16:19,390 --> 00:16:23,480
is expressing gratitude to others especially this one:
是向他人表达感激之情 尤其是这种方法

