00:16:50,130 --> 00:16:52,500
send the letter,make that phone call.
那就把信寄出去再打电话

300
00:16:52,730 --> 00:16:54,200
And before,just think for a few minutes,
致电前思考几分钟

301
00:16:54,400 --> 00:16:56,550
"what am I going to say? What am I really grateful for?"
"我要说些什么?我到底感激什么?"

302
00:16:57,480 --> 00:16:58,940
Again,whether it's to your parents,
不论是对你的父母

303
00:16:59,200 --> 00:17:00,080
whether it's to your friends,
或朋友

